    "Id": "chassisdef_ghostmaker_TRG-X5",
    "Name": "Ghostmaker",
    "Details": "The Ghostmaker balances heavy armor and average speed with overwhelming firepower. Its primary weapons are paired RAC-5s, each carrying five tons of ammo, allowing it to sustain prolonged combat. James’s skill ensures these rotary autocannons rarely jam, making them a formidable threat. Secondary weapons include four ER Medium Lasers and paired Medium Pulse and ER Small Lasers, providing solid short-to-medium range firepower in case of rotary jams. Twelve double heat sinks manage heat during intense firing, though James mainly relies on lasers as a backup. Despite its power, James is disappointed by the Ghostmaker’s lack of speed, limited by a 300 XL Fusion engine.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Accurate Weapon - AC</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.13</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
