  "StockRole": "Brawler",
  "YangsThoughts": "Melody’s Rockers, one of the few mercenary commands to survive the Jihad, continues serving clients under the legendary James Degenhardt. Now in his 80s, James still designs and tests custom ’Mechs, leaving heavy lifting to trusted young pilots. His persistence led to the creation of the Ghostmaker, a fully custom design like the Impaler and Crossfire. The Ghostmaker combines Marauder IIC legs with a heavily reinforced Targe chassis. It offers average speed for a heavy ’Mech, thick armor, and devastating medium-range firepower, making it a formidable adversary on the battlefield.",
